meta.description: BigBrotherBot (B3) is a cross-platform, cross-game game administration bot. Features in-game administration of game servers, multiple user access levels, and database storage. Currently include parsers for Call of Duty 1 to 8, Urban Terror (ioUrT 4.1 and 4.2), BF3, Arma II, CS:GO, Red Orchestra 2, BFBC2, MOH 2010, World of Padman, ETpro, Smokin' Guns, HomeFront, Open Arena, Altitude
